comment: Android-added: Add a LibcoreAnchor class to track the extra states.

variables.name: nativeAnchor
variables.comment:
* Stores the raw stack frames initialized by ART.
             * The frames are referenced here to avoid being GC-ed.
             * See BuildInternalStackTraceVisitor for the details in the art/runtime/thread.cc.

variables.name: stackLevel
variables.comment: * Tracks the stack level that have been processed and returned.
